I would HIGHLY suggest you also look into a powerpoint that we also put in to see how the code works if you are confused.

***IMPORTANT***
Please also email me (moon_hwan_kim@brown.edu) if you want to test the application. I need to put you as a test user in order to give you login functionality. You also need a facebook account for this.


Please make sure you have the following libraries installed. Please also make sure to keep the versions the same. 
	"async": "^3.2.0",
    "bcrypt-nodejs": "0.0.3",
