Please make sure you have the MongoDB database running on your local device. Or else the information will not save to your database. I suggest install robomongo and setting up a server. 


Then type npm start into terminal and go to localhost at port 8000

Do not be scared if you see a picture of one of our lovely teammates as your profile picture. This was a placeholder.


